rComments: From what I could tell, she's a tougher grader than a lot of the other SPCM teachers, but I got a lot out of the class.  It was fun and interesting.  You can easily get a B, but you have to work for an A.  It seems like she also grades based on your improvement, so you don't have to be an amazing speaker in order to get an A.
she is a tough grader but its an ok class
